latestIgtvVideos.caption:

Copenhagen and New York showgoers alike proved that all-over brown is a trend worth investing in, and now it's clear that primary and secondary colors like kelly green, fire-engine red, and Pantone's 2020 color of the year, classic blue, are also becoming street style mainstays worn color-blocked together.”

latestIgtvVideos.title: Monochrome outfit ideas!!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Monochrome looks!!
.
Hey guys!

Here’s presenting to you some monochrome outfit ideas. 
The word ‘mono’ means single and ‘chromatic’ means Color. 
So, monochromatic outfits would consist of pieces of different shades and tints of of same color, to create an overall tonal look.
I have intentionally not included all black, all white snd all grey look. I have included interesting color pallete here. 
The funda is to incorporate textures and fabrics into your outfit to create depth and add interest.

Don’t be shy to go for single colour from head to toe.!! They make you look taller n slimer , chic n stylish! In one word- 
stand out!! The monochrome looks
1. Sporty pink
2. Mustard yellow
3. Olive green

Roses 🌹 

Sikkim is known for its beautiful blooms ! 💐

After breakfast we head out for a quick stroll just outside our homestay in pakyong! 
Best time is spring summer when they are in full bloom. 🌹
south Sikkim- Namchi features over 50 varieties of roses, including hybrid tea, floribunda, and Grandiflora roses.

 A peaceful escape and stunning views of the surrounding mountains and valley!

latestPosts.caption:
⛰️

We drove at 3.30am from our hotel room to witness Kanchenjenga range at sunrise at 4.30 am . 
After days of  fogs and clouds covering the sight of Kanchenjunga, we finally got lucky to witness it on the last day of trip at Tiger hills, Darjeeling.
 Kanchenjunga  is world’s third-highest peak- a prominent feature of the Himalayan landscape visible from Tiger Hill.  
This viewpoint is a popular tourist destination, particularly for witnessing the sunrise over Kanchenjunga. 
 At sunrise, the peaks of Kanchenjunga are bathed in golden light, creating a breathtaking view. 

#Kanchenjunga #darjeeling #northeast #northeastindia #kanchenjungaview #mountainviews #tigerhills #sunrise

latestPosts.caption:
Chasing peace ☮️🕊️✌️😌

On a quiet hill 23 km from Gangtok, 
Rumtek Monastery is  largest monasteries in Sikkim. Also known as the Dharma Chakra Centre, it is the seat-in-exile of the Karmapa, the head of the Karma Kagyu lineage of Tibetan Buddhism.

It also houses-
Nalanda institute is one of the most iconic names in the history of education — both ancient and modern.

—making it not only a sacred site but also a cultural marvel.

#sikkim #gangtok #rumtekmonastery #sikkimtourism #nakandauniversity

latestPosts.caption:
Thukpa date in Gangtok! Yes plz! 🍜

We ducked into a tiny spot off MG Marg, chasing for food from all the travelling in the day — and found it in a bowl of thukpa at a local food joint. 

Rich, comforting, with just the right kick. Sikkim knows how to do soul food right. 🍜✨ n calling it a night night! 🌌

 #ThukpaInGangtok #SoulInABowl 
#thukpaDinnerDate #sikkimFood #gangtok #sikkumtourism

latestPosts.caption:
Sikkim is magic carved into the mountains ! And so glad to witness it 🏔️

Driving throw the hair-pin bend cliffs , seeing huge mountain peaks, winding roads, and valleys that steal your breath—. From the icy blues of Tsomgo & Changu Lake to the golden calm of Nathang, Tukla & Lungthang Valleys, every view felt like a living postcard. 
And nothing beats the joy of hot Maggi & momos served at 13,000 ft—with the clouds as company
and the Himalayas as your backdrop. 🏔️
❄️🍜

 #SikkimLove #northeastIndia #MountainsAndMomos #incredibleIndia #sikkim #gangtok #mountainmaggi #changulake #lyngthsngLake #gangtok #tsomgoLake #indiatourism
